
***** GetImageFromX: snapshot of a surface drawing window *******

token(s):
T_GetImageFromX		GetImageFromX

rule(s):
image <-- VAR_SURFDRAW  '.' T_GetImageFromX


parameters
  # VAR_SURFDRAW

description:
Save the snapshot as a 2D image of format RGB.
In the case of an image, the snapshot is taken from X11
as opposed to getimage, which takes the image using 
OpenGL.



See Also:
	getimage


